title: What A Wonderful Savior!
presentation: v1 c v2 c v3 c v4 c v5 c v6 c

v1: Christ has a full redemption made:
We are redeemed! the price is paid:
v2: I praise Him for the cleansing blood,
That reconciled my soul to God,
v3: He cleansed my heart from all its sin:
And now He reigns and rules therein;
v4: He dwells within me day by day,
And keeps me faithful all the way,
v5: And triumph in each trying hour,
v6: To Him I've given all my heart,
The world shall never share a part,
c1: What a wonderful Savior is Jesus my Savior;
What a wonderful Savior is Jesus my Lord!
